No. 671. The Consolidation Coal Company, Petitioner, v. American Mail Steamship Company, Claimant; and The Consolidation Coal Company, Claimant, Petitioner, v. American Mail Steamship Company. No. 672. April 16, 1906. Mr. J. Walter Lord and Mr. Edward S. Dodge for petitioner. Mr. Wilhelmus Mynderse and Mr. Edward E. Blodgett for respondents.

Petitions for writs of certiorari to the United States *649Circuit Court of Appeals for the First Circuit denied.
